criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Women of reproductive age (15-49 years) who reside in the study areas;

          2. Women who are prepared for pregnancy in 1-3 months or have already been pregnant for
             less than 20 months;

          3. Women who have provided written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Women who have already taken supplements containing vitamin B complex, iron, or folic
             acid for more than two weeks at enrollment;

          2. Women who have given birth to children with congenital heart disease or other birth
             defects before;

          3. Women with diabetes;

          4. women with severe heart, liver or kidney disease.
